summary: This dispatch transmits blank documents, including a City of Newark, New Jersey Birth Certificate, a New York driver's license instruction sheet, a National Geographic Travel-Lite Series blank Identity Card, a Flamingo Hotel identity Card, a blank Social Security card, a cachet of the Department of Labor of the Commonwealth of Puerto Rico with ink pad and assorted cellophane sheets used for lamination.
title: Transmittal of Blank Documentatia
